Main Navigation Hub
This section provides a core architecture and screen hierarchy overview for the rental platform.

Initial Landing: The Main Dashboard serves as the primary entry point.

Inventory List: Accessible via the sidebar navigation, leading to Property Listings.

Support Hub: Contains detailed information such as Agent Profiles.

2. Interactive Callouts
Specific behaviors triggered by user actions within the interface.

01. View Details Interaction: Clicking "View Details" on any Property Card triggers a horizontal slide-in transition from the right, overlaying 60% of the screen.

Trigger: On Tap.

02. Search Expansion: Focusing the search bar expands the filtering dropdown with a "Smart Animate" spring effect (300ms).

Trigger: On Focus.

3. Transition Definitions
Standardized timing and curves for all platform animations.

figma link: https://www.figma.com/design/etd3BGQdLekZhZgCy59NYF/Create-Interactive-Prototype?m=auto&t=QiJAuHsbcwE39Adj-6